# Test Rules 📋
1. ALWAYS use ./sled/scripts/test-runner.sh --all for full test suite
2. NEVER bypass the test runner
3. ALL tests MUST be in their designated directories
4. ALL tests MUST follow naming patterns
5. NO TypeScript - JavaScript only

